   <name>Basic packages for the game</name>
                <summary>Packages required for the beginner.</summary>
                <description>This package includes:
                  - steam
                  - gamemoded
                  - lutris</description>

                  <name lang="tr_TR">Oyun için temel paketler</name>
                <summary lang="tr_TR">Başlangıç için gerekli paketler.</summary>
                <description lang="tr_TR">Şunları İçerir:
                  - steam
                  - gamemoded
                  - lutris</description>
    <repositories>
    <repository recommended="true">
        <name>openSUSE:Tumbleweed:NonFree</name>
        <summary>Non Free parts of openSUSE Tumbleweed distribution.</summary>
        <description>Non free or non open source parts of openSUSE Tumbleweed.</description>
         <summary lang="tr_TR">openSUSE Tumbleweed dağıtımının Ücretsiz olmayan kısımları.</summary>
        <description lang="tr_TR">openSUSE Tumbleweed dağıtımının Ücretsiz olmayan kısımları.</description>
        <url>http://download.opensuse.org/tumbleweed/repo/non-oss/</url>
      </repository>

      <repository recommended="true">
        <name>openSUSE:Tumbleweed</name>
        <summary>Tumbleweed</summary>
        <description>Tumbleweed is the openSUSE Rolling Release

This OBS Project represents the content of the currently published
